    "body": "<p style=\"text-align: left !important;\">Bales of plastic No. 2 are piled on top of each other at the recycling facility at Neville Island.</p> \n\n<p style=\"text-align: left !important;\">Waste Management says it has identified domestic customers who buy and reuse these plastics to make new products.</p>",
